<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_232" id="115r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_232_r1l15">Frawen Elıſabeth Marggrefinn ʒu Brandemburg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l16">vnd <expan>Burggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>awen</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_232_r1l17">Gnedıge frawe als vns eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der hub </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l18">vnd <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe etlıch dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Jnnenhabe<ex>n</ex></expan> dauon ſıe <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l19">ʒu dıenen ſchuldıg <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l20">tun <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> der neẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l21">ʒwen ſein vnd auch <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıe dıe ſache antrıft für vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l22">beſandt vnd <expan>ſou<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> mit Jn geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Daʒ ſie Jrſelbs <expan>bottſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l23"><expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun werden . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>durchleẅchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l24">fleıſſ . daʒ ſıch eẅr gnade vmb <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dıenſt <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> in den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l25">ſachen <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> welle als wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_line_1577178064549_150">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_232_r1l28"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nıca<ex>m</ex></expan> Oculȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_232" id="115r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawen Elisabeth, marggrefinn zu Brandemburg und
                            <expan>burggrefin<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>awen</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige frawe, als uns ewr <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von der hub und
                                <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die etlich die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>innenhabe<ex>n</ex></expan>, davon sie <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> zu dienen schuldig
                                <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und tun <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, der newr zwen sein, und auch
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>,
                        die die sache antrift, für uns besandt und <expan>sov<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        mit in geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz sie irselbs
                                <expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> tun werden. <expan>Bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir ewr <expan>durchlewchtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, daz sich ewr
                        gnade umb <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> dienst
                            <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> in den sachen
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan> welle, als wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> etc. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und
                            <expan>wolgefall<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> oculi.</ab>
</div>
